{"tid":1996841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍至今發出逾350張限聚令告票 對比其他政府部門多出7倍","createTime":"2020-05-01T08:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:12:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7743dd6939b68855be64e1c222d318289dbf55","tid":1996841,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"警方至今發出逾350張限聚令告票<br />\n01.05.2020 16:18<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，截至零時，多個部門就限聚令巡查超過6.1萬次，警方共發出357張定額罰款告票，作出14宗檢控，及9000多次勸喻。<br />\n<br />\n至於規管食肆的規例，各部門共巡查餐飲業務處所超過7.7萬次，作出59宗檢控及2900多次勸喻。而針對需停業的遊戲機中心及浴室等處所，並作出2宗檢控及63次勸喻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284563&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284563%26csid%3D261_341&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=84562e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284563&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"db0c5e8726e2f18296f2fbbd8e00973f0eb632af","tid":1996841,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"咁係黑警濫告定其他部門失職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f73a141204a212315ffaee48cf91d9e94e4c78","tid":1996841,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"睇下有幾多張交再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f06b30e51a5807d20b8d683373424c0c0296e8","tid":1996841,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"唔籌期邊有錢派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acf37827f170d7e9b24556f90aeab9d8f9fac7f","tid":1996841,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"一個人都犯果啲根本亂黎"},{"p